    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term for secure chests or arks intended to contain the remains of the deceased, used particularly for such chests from ancient Greek, Etruscan, and Egyptian cultures.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
